{"tid":462081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又墜機！日本一架直升機墜落導致機上4人死亡","createTime":"2017-11-08T08:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T11:32:47.000Z","uid":141461,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"14f18e13c8499ec9c4c43d0e0ef63da8e8f4adcd","tid":462081,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/164435_5a6ce3c78bd9e11ace5fe933fdf2843b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F164435_5a6ce3c78bd9e11ace5fe933fdf2843b.jpg&h=653bdbf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地時間8日下午3點半左右，在日本群馬縣上野村乙母的藤澤橋附近，一架軍用直升機發生墜落事故。據當地消防人員稱，直升機墜落後起火，機上4人已全部死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據日本NHK新聞報道，據當地警方稱，8日下午，在日本群馬縣上野村，日本自衛隊一架直升機發生墜落事故，機上至少乘坐了4人。據消防人員表示，4人已經死亡。墜落的直升機是運送物資的大型軍用直升機。"},{"pid":"3de2841e3ba3ab2474c7effdfba4a2e75316e2a9","tid":462081,"uid":4288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"諗起日本航空123<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bf9df641212fc28b2e53a59148fd07b31b0e0c","tid":462081,"uid":2337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:02:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起日本航空123<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4f44ea612394143d3846418fbb366ea79d7578","tid":462081,"uid":29887,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:47:57.000Z","msg":"做乜唔用降落傘"},{"pid":"2a173ad49c3b9614174b135e6d301f7b60aba1c9","tid":462081,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T10:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f984903b729d2478ed538b500f5e0478f32412","tid":462081,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img